    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain utilizes a variable M differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. This example is mechanically sound, having undergone preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The chassis remains taut, featuring Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a multi-link rear suspension that maintains factory-spec kinematics. A well-sorted driver's car that balances track-ready engineering with daily usability.",
