      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit is equipped with a traditional 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term reliability, the VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates\u2014addressing the known weak points of this chassis. The engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline with crisp throttle response provided by the individual throttle bodies. The suspension retains its composure with updated bushings and a precise steering rack. While the finish reflects its history as a driver's car, the drivetrain and structural integrity remain excellent for the next owner seeking a pure analog performance machine.",
